<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar-no-user') %>

  <header>
    <div id="webpage-big-picture">
      <div class="carousel-inner">
        <!-- Slide One - Set the background image for this slide in the line below -->
        <div class="carousel-item active" style="background-color: #52796f">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4 text-white mt-5 mb-2 welcome">Conation</h1>
            <p class="lead mb-5 text-white-50 welcome2">Support now, reap the benefits later.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <div class="container" >
    <h1 class="my-4 welcome">Features</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
        <div class="card h-100 welcome2">
          <h4 class="card-header">Stay Local</h4>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">Local businesses have been hit hard by this pandemic.</p>
            <p class="card-text">Find out which small businesses are still open near you, and to what capacity you can provide your help.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4 welcome2">
        <div class="card h-100">
          <h4 class="card-header">Quick and Easy</h4>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">We provide a platform for small local business owners to bring their store online and reach customers as easily as possible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4 welcome2">
        <div class="card h-100">
          <h4 class="card-header">Get Started</h4>
          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">Click the button below to get started with Conation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <a href="/registration" class="btn btn-main float-right">Sign Up</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /.row -->

    

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <div class="row my-3" id="about">
      <div class="col-lg-6 enterLeft">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p class="lead">Conation strives to help business hit hardest by COVID-19.</p>
        <p>Small business owners are being heavily impacted by the current global pandemic. </p>
        <p>Often beloved, and very important to their local community; local businesses define a neighbourhood’s character and have close relationships with regular customers.</p>
        <p>Unfortunately, staying in business is difficult for these local businesses, as they cannot operate as they usually do. Our application gives each community a way to support their favourite businesses so that they won’t be forced to close.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6 enterRight">
        <img class="img-fluid rounded img-right" src="src/images/Conation_logo.png" alt="conation logo">
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- /.row -->

    <hr>
  </div>
  <!-- /.container -->

